<div style="clear:both;"></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both; border: solid #df0000; border-width: 1px 1px 0; background: #df0000; color: White; padding: .1em;padding-top: .1em;padding-left: .1em;padding-right: .1em;padding-bottom: .1em;text-align: center;font-family: sans-serif;font-size:100%;margin-bottom: 0px;">
<div class="plainlinks" style="float:right;margin-bottom:.1em;font-size:80%; color: White"><a class="external text" href="../../w/index-title=Portal_Socialism_Selected_quote_1&action=edit.php.html"><span style="color: White">edit</span></a>&#160;&#160;</div>
<h2 style="font-size:100%; font-weight:bold; border: none; margin: 0; padding:0; padding-bottom:.1em; color:White;"><span class="mw-headline" id="Selected_quote">Selected quote</span></h2>
</div>
<div style="border: 1px solid #df0000; border-top-width: 1px; vertical-align: top;background: #f9f9ff;opacity: 1; color: black; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 1em;padding-top: .3em;">
<p><br /></p>
<table class="cquote" style="margin:auto; border-collapse: collapse; border: none; background-color: transparent; width: auto;">
<tr>
<td width="20" valign="top" style="border:none; color:#B2B7F2;font-size:35px;font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; padding: 10px 10px;">“</td>
<td valign="top" style="border: none; padding: 4px 10px;">
<center>A free health service is pure Socialism and as such it is opposed to the hedonism of capitalist society.</center>
</td>
<td width="20" valign="bottom" style="border: none; color: #B2B7F2; font-size: 35px; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; padding: 10px 10px;">”</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3" class="cquotecite" style="border: none; padding-right: 4%">
<p style="font-size: smaller; text-align: right;"><cite style="font-style: normal;">—<a href="Aneurin_Bevan" title="Aneurin Bevan">Aneurin Bevan</a>, sixteenth <a href="Secretary_of_State_for_Health" title="Secretary of State for Health">U.K. Minister of Health</a>, <i>In Place of Fear</i>, 1952</cite></p>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<div style="clear:both;"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="width:44%;display:block;float:right;">
<div style="clear: both; border: solid #df0000; border-width: 1px 1px 0; background: #df0000; color: White; padding: .1em;padding-top: .1em;padding-left: .1em;padding-right: .1em;padding-bottom: .1em;text-align: center;font-family: sans-serif;font-size:100%;margin-bottom: 0px;">
<div class="plainlinks" style="float:right;margin-bottom:.1em;font-size:80%; color: White"><a class="external text" href="../../w/index-title=Portal_Socialism_Selected_picture_1&action=edit.php.html"><span style="color: White">edit</span></a>&#160;&#160;</div>
<h2 style="font-size:100%; font-weight:bold; border: none; margin: 0; padding:0; padding-bottom:.1em; color:White;"><span class="mw-headline" id="Selected_picture">Selected picture</span></h2>
</div>
<div style="border: 1px solid #df0000; border-top-width: 1px; vertical-align: top;background: #f9f9ff;opacity: 1; color: black; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 1em;padding-top: .3em;">
<div class="center">
<div class="floatnone"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Defending_Socialism_-_Street_Scene_-_Pinar_del_Rio_-_Cuba.JPG" class="image"><img alt="Defending Socialism - Street Scene - Pinar del Rio - Cuba.JPG" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/29/Defending_Socialism_-_Street_Scene_-_Pinar_del_Rio_-_Cuba.JPG/280px-Defending_Socialism_-_Street_Scene_-_Pinar_del_Rio_-_Cuba.JPG" width="280" height="373" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/29/Defending_Socialism_-_Street_Scene_-_Pinar_del_Rio_-_Cuba.JPG/420px-Defending_Socialism_-_Street_Scene_-_Pinar_del_Rio_-_Cuba.JPG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/29/Defending_Socialism_-_Street_Scene_-_Pinar_del_Rio_-_Cuba.JPG/560px-Defending_Socialism_-_Street_Scene_-_Pinar_del_Rio_-_Cuba.JPG 2x" /></a></div>
</div>
<center><small>Photo credit: <a href="http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/user:Adam63" class="extiw" title="meta:user:Adam63">Adam Jones</a></small> Defending socialism -- a street scene in Pinar del Rio, Cuba. December 2006.</center>
